How to Use
Browse Games:
Navigate to the Browse page to see a grid of all games with their details.

Add a Game:
Click on the Add Game link in the navigation bar.
Fill in the form with the game details and submit.

Edit a Game:
On the Browse page, click the Edit button on a game card.
Update the game details in the form and submit.

Delete a Game:
On the Browse page, click the Delete button on a game card to remove it permanently.
